{"tid":916700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次證明含撚派已經徹底收皮","createTime":"2018-11-26T01:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T01:43:12.000Z","uid":65457,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62fd3fa5b5278941a93d77988fab3206399f9dbb","tid":916700,"uid":65457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:23:08.000Z","msg":"對比番2016年九龍西既結果 其實今次販民差唔多吸番晒上次自己既票<br />\n如果將換屆選舉果時 吳文遠 6811 毛孟靜32323 譚國僑15383 黃碧雲26037 劉小麗38183 <br />\n加埋總共係118737 <br />\n而補選不嬲投票率會低少少<br />\n所以今次李卓人同馮檢基加埋有105566<br />\n已經接近係吸晒係2016年拎到既販民票<br />\n而游B同教主係2016年拎到果4萬票 佢地完全拎唔到<br />\n<br />\n亦即係話 今次真係冇人出黎含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n販民即管繼續屌票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保住關鍵一席 邊個唔投邊個就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148720f4b5b27d60d46ef7fa32576be5f5246d68","tid":916700,"uid":65457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"補番link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2016/chi/rs_gc_LC2.html?1543193904249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Flegco2016%2Fchi%2Frs_gc_LC2.html%3F1543193904249&d=azl4pq8h0FMwvaZgJeX2tkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=5dd62b93\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2016/chi/rs_gc_LC2.html?1543193904249</a>"},{"pid":"173efedd4831b2fb19185f243b031af4535053d1","tid":916700,"uid":522,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T01:28:12.000Z","msg":"90後已經都差唔多30歲, 成為社會主力 , 泛民仲要同本土派割席, 收皮是正常"},{"pid":"b25a529850b88b2a37c34473c3f77462f8145558","tid":916700,"uid":65457,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"173efedd4831b2fb